== Duality ==

=== Alternating operators ===
Given two vector spaces &quot;V&quot; and &quot;X&quot; and a natural number &quot;k&quot;, an alternating operator from &quot;V&quot;&quot;k&quot; to &quot;X&quot; is a multilinear map
